00:00:49.423 --> 00:00:49.990 position:38% line:89% align:start
[splat]

00:00:54.026 --> 00:00:56.427 position:10% line:89% align:start
Charming little creatures...

00:01:02.530 --> 00:01:04.899 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>...our earthly little</i>
 <i>cockroaches.</i>

00:01:04.932 --> 00:01:07.533 position:38% line:89% align:start
[squish]

00:01:07.566 --> 00:01:10.635 position:7% line:83% align:start
People on this planet are so
blissfully unaware.

00:01:10.835 --> 00:01:12.436 position:33% line:89% align:start
[crunching]

00:01:14.303 --> 00:01:16.938 position:7% line:77% align:start
 <i>On Mars we have to watch our </i>
 <i>every step, or the roaches</i>
 <i>exterminate us.  </i>

00:01:17.939 --> 00:01:19.973 position:38% line:89% align:start
[smash]

00:01:20.007 --> 00:01:21.941 position:41% line:89% align:start
[roar]

00:01:23.042 --> 00:01:24.710 position:5% line:5% align:start
(MARCOS) <i>It wasn't after Sheila</i>

00:01:25.543 --> 00:01:27.310 position:5% line:5% align:start
 <i>They're trying to get the serum.</i>

00:01:27.944 --> 00:01:31.579 position:7% line:5% align:start
 <i>They must know, without it, we</i>
 <i>can't mutate!</i>

00:01:31.947 --> 00:01:35.749 position:5% line:5% align:start
 <i>Dammit! We're sitting ducks we </i>
 <i>gotta move!</i>

00:01:36.916 --> 00:01:40.952 position:33% line:89% align:start
[whimpering]

00:01:40.985 --> 00:01:42.652 position:27% line:89% align:start
Hang on tight!

00:01:42.685 --> 00:01:43.853 position:38% line:89% align:start
[reving]

00:01:43.886 --> 00:01:45.620 position:33% line:89% align:start
[shattering]

00:01:46.353 --> 00:01:47.022 position:41% line:89% align:start
[thud]

00:01:49.589 --> 00:01:51.490 position:38% line:89% align:start
Bastard

00:01:51.523 --> 00:01:54.625 position:5% line:77% align:start
 <i>It must've been clinging to the</i>
 <i>bottom of the ship </i>
 <i>this whole time.</i>

00:01:54.992 --> 00:01:57.561 position:10% line:83% align:start
 <i>Hiding right in our radar's</i>
 <i>blind spot.</i>

00:01:58.095 --> 00:02:00.628 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>We better take care of it before</i>
 <i>more of them show up.</i>

00:02:02.362 --> 00:02:05.531 position:10% line:83% align:start
Marcos, Keiji, c'mon! Bring
serum and nets.

00:02:05.765 --> 00:02:06.331 position:41% line:89% align:start
Right!

00:02:06.364 --> 00:02:06.899 position:41% line:89% align:start
Right.

00:02:08.633 --> 00:02:11.534 position:7% line:77% align:start
 <i>The rest of you, stay out of </i>
 <i>sight and</i>
 <i>do not leave the vehicle!</i>

00:02:22.640 --> 00:02:23.608 position:55% line:89% align:start
 <i>This roach...</i>

00:02:24.542 --> 00:02:25.043 position:64% line:89% align:start
...is ours.

00:03:56.893 --> 00:04:01.862 position:41% line:5% align:start
04 WAR

00:04:03.663 --> 00:04:07.498 position:10% line:83% align:start
(SHOKICHI) <i>It looks like our</i>
 <i>virus sample... is right here.</i>

00:04:11.668 --> 00:04:14.103 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>Time to inject and mutate.</i>

00:04:14.136 --> 00:04:17.404 position:5% line:83% align:start
(MARCOS) <i>Wha- But the manual, It</i>
 <i>says if  there's just one-</i>

00:04:17.437 --> 00:04:20.773 position:13% line:77% align:start
(SHOKICHI) <i>Forget the damn</i>
 <i>manual these things are</i>
 <i>unpredictable...</i>

00:04:21.140 --> 00:04:23.507 position:10% line:89% align:start
We use every means possible.

00:04:40.751 --> 00:04:41.551 position:41% line:89% align:start
[Hiss]

00:04:42.417 --> 00:04:43.685 position:80% line:89% align:start
Huh?!

00:04:43.718 --> 00:04:44.686 position:5% line:89% align:start
A decoy?

00:04:44.719 --> 00:04:46.554 position:41% line:89% align:start
[buzz]

00:04:46.587 --> 00:04:48.454 position:41% line:89% align:start
[thud]

00:04:48.488 --> 00:04:50.389 position:35% line:89% align:start
[gasping]

00:04:51.824 --> 00:04:54.457 position:33% line:89% align:start
[crinkling]

00:04:54.491 --> 00:04:54.858 position:33% line:89% align:start
[chittering]

00:04:54.891 --> 00:04:55.725 position:38% line:89% align:start
[squeak]

00:04:57.026 --> 00:04:57.626 position:7% line:83% align:start
(SHOKICHI) <i>They're going after</i>
 <i>the escape vehicle!</i>

00:05:07.165 --> 00:05:08.465 position:35% line:89% align:start
[screech]

00:05:08.499 --> 00:05:09.133 position:27% line:89% align:start
[sharp inhales]

00:05:12.534 --> 00:05:14.002 position:7% line:89% align:start
[insect-like chirping noises]

00:05:18.071 --> 00:05:26.210 position:16% line:89% align:start
[heavy fearful panting]

00:05:26.243 --> 00:05:28.877 position:7% line:83% align:start
You've almost got it, Sheila.
The sight's over here.

00:05:29.778 --> 00:05:30.945 position:27% line:89% align:start
Look, like this.

00:05:33.213 --> 00:05:36.948 position:5% line:71% align:start
 <i>Your M.A.R.S. Ranking is an 89,</i>
 <i>so you'll need to use your </i>
 <i>brains over brawn with the</i>
 <i>roaches. </i>

00:05:37.582 --> 00:05:43.384 position:7% line:77% align:start
Learn how to properly use the
net. Your life or a teammate's
may one day depend on it.

00:05:44.552 --> 00:05:45.752 position:27% line:89% align:start
See you on Mars.

00:05:49.055 --> 00:05:49.989 position:35% line:89% align:start
Capturing!

00:05:53.557 --> 00:06:00.493 position:10% line:71% align:start
(NARRATOR) <i>The net is one of</i>
 <i>humankind's simplest but most</i>
 <i>ingenious inventions. Its uses</i>
 <i>are nearly limitless. </i>

00:06:00.761 --> 00:06:04.129 position:10% line:83% align:start
 <i>From natural materials like</i>
 <i>cotton and hemp,</i>

00:06:04.163 --> 00:06:10.633 position:33% line:71% align:start
 <i>to stronger</i>
 <i>rupture-resistant synthetics,</i>
 <i>netting has evolved in parallel</i>
 <i>with humanity. </i>

00:06:10.666 --> 00:06:14.635 position:5% line:89% align:start
[strainging gasps and squealing]

00:06:14.668 --> 00:06:16.237 position:13% line:89% align:start
You're not going anywhere!

00:06:16.270 --> 00:06:16.971 position:38% line:89% align:start
Captain!

00:06:18.872 --> 00:06:22.473 position:13% line:77% align:start
(NARRATOR) <i>The German-made</i>
 <i>Anti-Terraformar Net Launcher is</i>
 <i>designed to withstand... </i>

00:06:22.506 --> 00:06:25.008 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>...up to three times a </i>
 <i>terraformar's strength. </i>

00:06:25.041 --> 00:06:27.142 position:21% line:89% align:start
[struggling noises]

00:06:29.777 --> 00:06:31.612 position:19% line:89% align:start
Terraformar captured.

00:06:31.645 --> 00:06:33.246 position:38% line:89% align:start
[sighs]

00:06:33.279 --> 00:06:34.746 position:44% line:89% align:start
Well done, Sheila.

00:06:36.248 --> 00:06:38.983 position:7% line:77% align:start
Your quick thinking and your
bravery mean that the crew is
now safe.

00:06:41.084 --> 00:06:43.018 position:21% line:89% align:start
[inhale] Thank you!

00:06:45.186 --> 00:06:46.419 position:38% line:89% align:start
Marcos!

00:06:47.620 --> 00:06:50.755 position:10% line:83% align:start
Open the insect enclosure.
Help me throw this thing in.

00:06:50.788 --> 00:06:51.522 position:5% line:89% align:start
Right.

00:06:57.226 --> 00:06:59.060 position:41% line:89% align:start
[roar]

00:07:19.238 --> 00:07:20.572 position:7% line:89% align:start
(SHICHSEI) <i>I must tell you...</i>

00:07:22.340 --> 00:07:26.441 position:5% line:77% align:start
 <i>I'm here on orders from U-NASA </i>
 <i>to kill you, Honda.</i>
 <i>To ensure your silence. </i>

00:07:28.210 --> 00:07:30.211 position:7% line:89% align:start
(KOU) <i>Still resentful, I see.</i>

00:07:30.844 --> 00:07:34.779 position:5% line:83% align:start
All because of my contribution
to the Bugs Procedure no doubt?

00:07:35.546 --> 00:07:37.547 position:44% line:89% align:start
[scoff] <i>Naturally.</i>

00:07:38.648 --> 00:07:42.717 position:7% line:77% align:start
Although the Japanese public
seemed pleased enough
with the final outcome.

00:07:43.851 --> 00:07:48.654 position:7% line:77% align:start
But you and I both know that
the greatest threat to
inter-corporate competition

00:07:49.655 --> 00:07:52.455 position:7% line:83% align:start
...is the theft of classified
technology.

00:07:54.823 --> 00:07:56.791 position:7% line:83% align:start
(NARRATOR) <i>The culprit was not</i>
 <i>fire.</i>

00:08:00.160 --> 00:08:03.262 position:35% line:89% align:start
[inhaling]

00:08:03.296 --> 00:08:08.598 position:13% line:77% align:start
 <i>What tore a hole through </i>
 <i>Sheila's chest was a searing-hot</i>
 <i>weaponized vapor...</i>

00:08:08.631 --> 00:08:10.966 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>Hydrogen peroxide and</i>
 <i>hydroquinone.</i>

00:08:11.533 --> 00:08:13.768 position:33% line:89% align:start
Th-The Bugs Procedure!

00:08:14.235 --> 00:08:15.502 position:41% line:89% align:start
How?!

00:08:17.237 --> 00:08:20.872 position:5% line:83% align:start
(NARRATOR) <i>Shokichi Komachi knew</i>
 <i>the attack move well.</i>

00:08:20.905 --> 00:08:22.839 position:7% line:89% align:start
 <i>The bombardier beetle's spray.</i>

00:08:23.040 --> 00:08:28.475 position:5% line:77% align:start
 <i>The very same ability acquired </i>
 <i>by a Bugs 2 crew member</i>
 <i>twenty years ago. </i>

00:08:29.276 --> 00:08:31.177 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:08:31.210 --> 00:08:31.978 position:41% line:89% align:start
[plop]

00:08:32.011 --> 00:08:32.844 position:75% line:89% align:start
Sheila!

00:08:37.580 --> 00:08:38.715 position:86% line:89% align:start
Sis

00:08:40.115 --> 00:08:41.816 position:10% line:83% align:start
(SYLVESTER) <i>There's no doubt</i>
 <i>about it...It's enhanced.   </i>

00:08:43.884 --> 00:08:47.954 position:5% line:71% align:start
 <i>Its rapid movement is a remnant</i>
 <i>of The Bugs Procedure.</i>
 <i>That's the Rove beetle's</i>
 <i>ability! </i>

00:08:53.990 --> 00:09:01.794 position:5% line:71% align:start
(NARRATOR) <i>20 years ago, in the</i>
 <i>fight  against the terraformars,</i>
 <i>the  members of Bugs 2 became</i>
 <i>part of an experiment. </i>

00:09:02.161 --> 00:09:06.964 position:7% line:77% align:start
 <i>They were made human hybrids,</i>
 <i>their DNA spliced</i>
 <i>with various insects. </i>

00:09:07.297 --> 00:09:14.500 position:7% line:71% align:start
 <i>All with the hope of gaining </i>
 <i>an edge over the Martian </i>
 <i>cockroaches. All in the name of</i>
 <i>the unstealable weapon</i>

00:09:17.836 --> 00:09:18.570 position:33% line:89% align:start
 <i>But then...</i>

00:09:20.838 --> 00:09:21.838 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>The unthinkable...</i>

00:09:25.074 --> 00:09:31.110 position:10% line:89% align:start
[heavy breathing, growling]

00:09:31.143 --> 00:09:35.779 position:5% line:83% align:start
Let me go! Do you hear me?! It's
because you...[exhales]

00:09:43.117 --> 00:09:44.218 position:24% line:89% align:start
Please forgive me.

00:09:45.118 --> 00:09:48.187 position:5% line:83% align:start
Conserving the serum was a grave
 misstep.

00:09:49.253 --> 00:09:53.622 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:09:53.656 --> 00:09:57.192 position:10% line:83% align:start
I suggest you get up, sir.
Quickly. The enemy...

00:10:06.263 --> 00:10:08.630 position:41% line:89% align:start
[roar]

00:10:08.664 --> 00:10:10.798 position:35% line:89% align:start
[yelling]

00:10:10.832 --> 00:10:13.067 position:38% line:89% align:start
[thwack]

00:10:13.101 --> 00:10:17.869 position:27% line:89% align:start
[heavy panting]

00:10:18.069 --> 00:10:18.903 position:38% line:89% align:start
Sheila!

00:10:33.878 --> 00:10:35.313 position:35% line:89% align:start
[inhales]

00:10:35.346 --> 00:10:42.850 position:21% line:89% align:start
[struggling exhales]

00:10:43.117 --> 00:10:46.119 position:21% line:89% align:start
[strained breathing]

00:10:46.152 --> 00:10:47.085 position:5% line:89% align:start
(SHOKICHI) <i>Don't...</i>

00:10:47.119 --> 00:10:47.819 position:35% line:89% align:start
[whimpers]

00:10:48.420 --> 00:10:49.253 position:5% line:89% align:start
 <i>You'll only make it worse.</i>

00:10:51.087 --> 00:10:52.255 position:38% line:89% align:start
Captain!

00:10:52.288 --> 00:10:54.790 position:35% line:89% align:start
[whimpers]

00:10:54.823 --> 00:10:55.757 position:5% line:89% align:start
Please just listen

00:10:57.058 --> 00:10:57.958 position:64% line:89% align:start
 <i>Sheila was</i>

00:10:58.892 --> 00:11:00.726 position:16% line:89% align:start
(SHEILA) <i>I was wondering</i>

00:11:00.760 --> 00:11:01.093 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:11:02.128 --> 00:11:03.928 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>Could you teach me something in </i>
 <i>Japanese?</i>

00:11:04.396 --> 00:11:09.164 position:5% line:83% align:start
Well, it depends. Are you trying
to woo the captain?

00:11:09.731 --> 00:11:11.799 position:5% line:89% align:start
 <i>Oh, this is too good.</i>

00:11:11.832 --> 00:11:12.532 position:35% line:89% align:start
[chortle]

00:11:13.700 --> 00:11:15.634 position:13% line:89% align:start
(EVA) <i>Just teach her already!</i>

00:11:19.803 --> 00:11:27.241 position:5% line:89% align:start
[struggling to speak, whimpers]

00:11:28.275 --> 00:11:33.911 position:19% line:71% align:start
(AKARI) <i>All right, all</i>
 <i>right...So you  want to profess</i>
 <i>your feelings to a Japanese guy,</i>
 <i>huh? </i>

00:11:34.378 --> 00:11:36.780 position:10% line:89% align:start
 <i>It's best to keep it simple.</i>

00:11:37.846 --> 00:11:41.581 position:7% line:83% align:start
 <i>Look him straight in the eyes</i>
 <i>and tell him how you feel</i>

00:11:42.316 --> 00:11:52.321 position:21% line:89% align:start
[laborous breathing]

00:11:52.355 --> 00:12:03.660 position:21% line:89% align:start
[laborous breathing]

00:12:03.693 --> 00:12:07.596 position:30% line:89% align:start
[long exhale]

00:12:08.097 --> 00:12:09.764 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:12:09.798 --> 00:12:11.099 position:5% line:89% align:start
(SHOKICHI) <i>I understand, Sheila.</i>

00:12:12.399 --> 00:12:14.200 position:30% line:89% align:start
I'm so sorry.

00:12:44.883 --> 00:12:47.885 position:10% line:83% align:start
(KOU) <i>I presume that you're</i>
 <i>attempting it again?</i>

00:12:47.919 --> 00:12:50.087 position:10% line:83% align:start
 <i>To a whole new group, a new</i>
 <i>crew?</i>

00:12:50.420 --> 00:12:52.822 position:19% line:89% align:start
The Bugs Procedure, I mean.

00:12:53.055 --> 00:12:57.024 position:5% line:83% align:start
Yeah, a tricky two part
operation, wasn't it?

00:12:57.723 --> 00:12:58.858 position:5% line:89% align:start
The Terraformar...

00:12:59.991 --> 00:13:03.461 position:5% line:83% align:start
The Terraformar Immunotolerance
Organ Transplantation,

00:13:03.494 --> 00:13:08.930 position:16% line:77% align:start
and the human-insect DNA
amalgamation operation are two
highly dangerous procedures.

00:13:09.331 --> 00:13:10.630 position:44% line:89% align:start
But you knew that.

00:13:11.332 --> 00:13:13.133 position:5% line:89% align:start
Ah, yes, of course.

00:13:14.200 --> 00:13:15.101 position:5% line:89% align:start
However...

00:13:16.469 --> 00:13:19.136 position:19% line:77% align:start
The surgery given to those
onboard the Annex 1
has a new name.

00:13:19.436 --> 00:13:22.704 position:7% line:83% align:start
It's no longer referred to as
the Bugs Procedure.

00:13:23.738 --> 00:13:23.839 position:69% line:89% align:start
 <i>Really?!</i>

00:13:27.307 --> 00:13:30.641 position:7% line:5% align:start
(SYLVESTER) <i>That roach wasn't</i>
 <i>alone because it was lost.</i>

00:13:31.076 --> 00:13:36.812 position:7% line:5% align:start
 <i>He's too highly skilled. That </i>
 <i>was a coordinated attack and we</i>
 <i>walked right into it. </i>

00:13:40.248 --> 00:13:43.816 position:7% line:83% align:start
Astounding! They've adopted a
hierarchy of leadership.

00:13:47.084 --> 00:13:51.020 position:7% line:83% align:start
Somehow, they figured out we
split into six groups...

00:13:52.921 --> 00:13:54.122 position:10% line:89% align:start
... <i>and our exact locations.</i>

00:13:58.190 --> 00:14:00.925 position:5% line:5% align:start
(SHOKICHI) <i>If these roaches have</i>
 <i>undergone  the Bugs Procedure...</i>

00:14:01.993 --> 00:14:06.928 position:13% line:77% align:start
 <i>They either stole it, or </i>
 <i>someone provided them with </i>
 <i>the Bugs 2 Technology. </i>

00:14:08.263 --> 00:14:09.131 position:38% line:89% align:start
Dammit.

00:14:10.697 --> 00:14:14.133 position:5% line:77% align:start
 <i>All that means is they've become</i>
 <i>even bigger pests, nothing</i>
 <i>more.</i>

00:14:16.067 --> 00:14:17.068 position:24% line:89% align:start
We have the edge.

00:14:18.269 --> 00:14:20.870 position:10% line:83% align:start
They're relying on outdated
technology!

00:14:21.070 --> 00:14:22.238 position:30% line:89% align:start
Akari, serum.

00:14:22.471 --> 00:14:23.938 position:19% line:89% align:start
Ivan! Down the hatch.

00:14:25.873 --> 00:14:29.342 position:7% line:77% align:start
(SHICHISEI) <i>The Bugs Procedure</i>
 <i>was insufficient, so we created</i>
 <i>a new operation called... </i>

00:14:31.476 --> 00:14:33.177 position:10% line:89% align:start
 <i>Artificial Metamorphosis...</i>

00:14:33.977 --> 00:14:35.944 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>Mosaic Organ Operation!</i>

00:14:45.183 --> 00:14:50.119 position:13% line:77% align:start
(AKARI) <i>You're vermin of a</i>
 <i>destitute planet. A planet with</i>
 <i>a deserted, arid past. </i>

00:14:51.354 --> 00:14:57.223 position:5% line:77% align:start
 <i>We come from Earth, a planet one</i>
 <i>million,  two hundred and fifty</i>
 <i>thousand species strong.  </i>

00:14:58.458 --> 00:15:00.125 position:19% line:89% align:start
So don't fuck with us!

00:15:12.798 --> 00:15:14.799 position:16% line:89% align:start
(KOU) <i>The Mosaic Organ?</i>

00:15:17.201 --> 00:15:22.204 position:10% line:71% align:start
 <i>Do you mean the terraformar</i>
 <i>immune tolerance organ that  was</i>
 <i>used in the Bugs Procedure</i>
 <i>twenty years ago? </i>

00:15:23.271 --> 00:15:24.005 position:10% line:89% align:start
(SHICHISEI) <i>That's correct.</i>

00:15:26.506 --> 00:15:31.276 position:19% line:71% align:start
 <i>It's what allowed the</i>
 <i>terraformars to mutate so</i>
 <i>drastically in as little as</i>
 <i>just five hundred years. </i>

00:15:32.276 --> 00:15:37.212 position:21% line:5% align:start
It's an evolutionary
development that brought us to
the next  level of gene
splicing. And we stole it.

00:15:37.778 --> 00:15:39.013 position:24% line:89% align:start
The mosaic organ.

